    "In Example 8 the model unsuccessfully attempts to format the query in a URL-like format, even though it has been provided with the necessary and ontology.",
    "Over the course of the iterations of self-improving prompts, the model did manage to produce queries that were syntactically correct.",
    "The query in Example 9 would be executable, except that the model added its own prefix, which does not match the IRI's in the underlying graph.",
    "Removing the incorrect prefix could be done in a post-processing step.",
    "The OPRO framework demonstrates that models can improve the prompts they are given, leading to better 3% results for 5 shots with respect to 1 shot (see Table 6)."
